### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/
Accept: application/json

### Create User
POST http://localhost:3001/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "preferences": "in-app"
}

### Create Event (like from user 1 to user 2)
POST http://localhost:3001/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "like",
  "source_user_id": 1,
  "target_user_id": 2,
  "data": "Liked post 123"
}

### Get Notifications for user 2
GET http://localhost:3001/notifications/2
Accept: application/json

### Mark Notification as Read
POST http://localhost:3001/notifications/1/read
Accept: application/json
